        <item>
            <title>Apple 终止 Epic Games 开发者帐号　Epic Games：Apple 向我们复仇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/epic-games-apple/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=epic-games-apple</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/epic-games-apple/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:05:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Epic Games]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222968</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，Apple 就欧洲数位市场法案（DMA）而被迫更改 App Store 条款，而 Epic Games 就计划使用帐户将 Epic Games Store 和 Fortnite 引入欧洲的 iOS 装置，却发现 Apple 终止了其开发者帐户。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222969 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/epicgamesstoreapple-694x445.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="445" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/epicgamesstoreapple-694x445.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/epicgamesstoreapple.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Epic Games 提出证据指很有可能因其公开批评 Apple 提出的 DMA 合规计划，而遭到 Apple 复仇</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Epic Games 昨（6 日）在官方网站发文指控 Apple 违反欧洲数位市场法案（DMA），认为 Apple 无意在 iOS 装置上允许真正的竞争。Epic Games 强烈谴责 Apple 正在消灭 App Store 的潜在竞争对手，亦削弱了 Epic Games 成为可竞争对手的能力。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Epic Games 提出证据指很有可能因其公开批评 Apple 提出的 DMA 合规计划，而遭到 Apple 复仇。Epic Games 最后强调：「我们将继续努力为欧洲和世界各地的 iOS 装置带来真正的竞争和选择。」</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.epicgames.com/site/en-US/news/apple-terminated-epic-s-developer-account">Epic Games</a>、<a href="https://overclock3d.net/news/software/apple-terminates-epic-games-developer-account-calling-them-untrustworthy/">OC3D</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/19/epic-games-store/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Epic Games 将重回 iOS　今年内推出 iOS 版 Epic Games Store</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/09/epic-disney/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">迪士尼向 Epic Games 投资 118 亿，冀发展 Fortnite 宇宙</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/18/apple-wants-epic-games-legal-expenses/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">反垄断官司尘埃落定   Apple 向 Epic Games 索取 7,340 万美元诉讼费</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/epic-games-apple/software/ios-app/">Apple 终止 Epic Games 开发者帐号　Epic Games：Apple 向我们复仇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
